ial Section  -->\r\n            <section data-padding data-bg=\"template\">\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n                    <div class=\"row align-items-md-center\">\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade\" class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--testimonial\">\r\n                                <div class=\"info\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"text\">\r\n                                        <p>Dear rule-breakers, questioners, straight-A students who skipped class: We want you.\r\n                                        </p>\r\n                                        <!-- <span class=\"author\">Martin Drew <em class=\"meta\">Head of Business Developer</em></span>\r\n                                        <img class=\"logo\" data-unveil src=\"#\" data-src=\"assets/img/logo-placeholder-2.png\" data-src-retina=\"assets/img/logo-placeholder-2@2x.png\" alt=\"\"> -->\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-delay=\"200\" class=\"col-md-5 offset-md-1\">\r\n                            <div class=\"wrapimage-element--square\">\r\n                                <img data-unveil src=\"#\" data-src=\"public/img/join-meeting.png\" data-src-retina=\"public/img/join-meeting.png\" alt=\"join meeting\">\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <!--  END: Testimonial Section  -->\r\n\r\n<section data-padding=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n                    <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"row aos-init aos-animate\" data-padding=\"xstop\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\r\n                            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">At Iron Buzz we subscribe to a set of beliefs that help guide how we work, play, and problem solve together. If these resonate for you, there just might be a role with your name on it.</p>\r\n                            <strong>Everybody can, and should, make a difference</strong>\r\n                                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Whether you’re fresh out of college or a seasoned executive, at Iron Buzz we expect you to go the extra mile and figure out how you can have the greatest impact in your role. Titles be damned.</p>\r\n                                <strong>Smart risks are worth taking</strong>\r\n                                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Look before leaping, yes—but then, by all means, leap. While we expect people to be thoughtful and strategic, to analyse all angles, we also know that real progress only comes from real risk taking. And when smart risks fail? We celebrate those too.</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\r\n                            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Holy grail bandwidth stealth niche market freemium buyer traction. A/B testing paradigm shift stealth return on investment android startup user experience bootstrapping funding partnership agile development innovator network\r\n                                effects. Beta series A financing buzz creative. </p>\r\n                                <strong>The ethical choice is the right one</strong>\r\n                                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Doing the right thing not only feels better, we think it pays off in the long run. Whether we’re choosing a project, being transparent to customers about our costs, or making sure our colleague is being treated fairly—there’s a right choice, and we want people to make it.</p>\r\n                                <strong>Less really is better</strong>\r\n                                <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">At Iron Buzz this means we make fewer things that last longer—but it also means that we encourage the team to focus on what really matters. We believe that doing one or two things really well goes a lot further than doing ten things only OK. </p>\r\n\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </section>\r\n\r\n\r\n        <!--  Testimonial Section  -->\r\n            <section data-padding data-bg=\"template\">\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n                    <div class=\"row align-items-md-center\">\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade\" class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--testimonial\">\r\n                                <div class=\"info\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"\">\r\n                                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iron Buzz provides Equal Employment Opportunities (EEO) to all employees and applicants for employment without regard to race, colour, religion, sex, national origin, age, disability, genetics, sexual orientation, gender identity or gender expression <strong>Are you in?</strong>  Check out the positions we are looking for and fill the form. \r\n                                        </p>\r\n                                        <h5 style=\"margin:10px 0px\">Manager </h5>\r\n                                        <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We’re looking for a manager for our studio, which manages the day-to-day operations between our artists and clients. We’re looking for someone who believes that each and every customer deserves world-class service and goes above and beyond to make sure that service is delivered. Studio managers have a demanding job, but the demands are worth the rewards. This is one of those rare opportunities where your work will help enrich others lives.</p>\r\n                                        <!-- <span class=\"author\">Martin Drew <em class=\"meta\">Head of Business Developer</em></span>\r\n                                        <img class=\"logo\" data-unveil src=\"#\" data-src=\"assets/img/logo-placeholder-2.png\" data-src-retina=\"assets/img/logo-placeholder-2@2x.png\" alt=\"\"> -->\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"zoom-in\" data-aos-delay=\"200\" class=\"col-md-5 offset-md-1\">\r\n                            <div class=\"wrapimage-element--square\">\r\n                                <img data-unveil src=\"#\" data-src=\"public/img/author-big.jpg\" data-src-retina=\"public/img/author-big.jpg\" alt=\"join meeting\">\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <!--  END: Testimonial Section  -->\r\n\r\n            <section data-padding=\"\">\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n                    <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"row aos-init aos-animate\" data-padding=\"xstop\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\r\n                             <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                            <h4>Your day-to-day:</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                        <li>Manage customer queries adhering to a daily schedule that includes a mix of: Phones, three (3) simultaneous chats, and emails ensuring clients have a quick response time with same-day replies</li>\r\n                                        <li>Delight our customers. You’ll pull out all the stops to deliver a memorable experience (in a “I can’t wait to tell my friends about this fabulous service” way)</li>\r\n                                        <li>Research social media platforms and generate reports for the same.</li>\r\n                                        <li>Additional store manager duties as needed</li>\r\n                                    </ul>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\r\n                             <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                            <h4>We’d love to hear from you if you have:</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                        <li>Proven track record in managing teams; distributed teams a plus</li>\r\n                                        <li>Excellent oral and written communication skills in English and Hindi. Not only will you talk to people on the phone, you’ll communicate with our customers  in writing as well. </li>\r\n                                        <li>Must have a friendly and welcoming nature.</li>\r\n                                        <li>Self-starter, who can work independently and enthusiastically to ensure customer success</li>\r\n                                        <li>Highly organised and detail-oriented</li>\r\n                                        <li>Applicants who are enthusiastic about the Tattoo business is a plus.</li>\r\n                                    </ul>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        \r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"sectiontitle-element\" style=\"text-align: center;     margin: 30px;\">\r\n                              <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn--big--round--border--dark\">Apply for this job</a>\r\n                            </div>\r\n            </section>\r\n\r\n            <!--  Intro Section  -->\r\n            <section>\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n                    <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"row\" data-padding=\"xstop\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\r\n                            <div class=\"sectiontitle-element--center\">\r\n                                <!-- <span class=\"toptitle\">What We Do</span> -->\r\n                                <h2>Head of Marketing</h2>\r\n                                <p>We are looking for a Head of Marketing who’ll lead all our marketing activities from social media and digital campaigns to advertising and creative projects.</p>\r\n\r\n                                <p>Head of Marketing responsibilities include developing plans to help establish our brand, allocating resources to different projects and setting short-term and long-term department goals. If you’re a skilled Marketing strategist, able to inspire your team members, we’d like to meet you.</p>\r\n\r\n                                <p>Ultimately, you will run our Marketing department in ways that promote higher profitability and competitiveness.</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"row\" data-padding=\"xstop\">\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"100\" class=\"col-12 col-md-8\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                                <h4>Your day-to-day:</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                        <li>Craft strategies for all Marketing teams, including Digital, Advertising, Communications and Creative</li>\r\n                                        <li>Prepare and manage monthly, quarterly and annual budgets for the Marketing department</li>\r\n                                        <li>Set, monitor and report on team goals</li>\r\n          