                   </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                       \r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"sectiontitle-element\" style=\"text-align: center;     margin: 30px;\">\r\n                              <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn--big--round--border--dark\">Apply for this job</a>\r\n                            </div>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <!--  END Intro Section  -->\r\n              <!--  Intro Section  -->\r\n            <section>\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n                    <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" class=\"row\" data-padding=\"xstop\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-12\">\r\n                            <div class=\"sectiontitle-element--center\">\r\n                                <!-- <span class=\"toptitle\">What We Do</span> -->\r\n                                <h2>Graphic Designer</h2>\r\n                                <p>We are looking for a Graphic Designer to join our creative team to help bring our brand to life and evolve our design vision. This role will contribute to a wide range of projects with work spanning both the digital and physical space—anything from email and site design to in-store signage and paid advertising is fair game. This position will work closely with the marketing team to develop, concept and execute brand campaigns.</p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"row\" data-padding=\"xstop\">\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"100\" class=\"col-12 col-md-4\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                                <h4>Your day-to-day:</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                        <li>Produce innovative and beautiful design solutions consistent with our brand image across site, social media, paid and physical channels</li>\r\n                                        <li>Collaborate with creative and marketing team members to create campaign-level work across multiple social media channels and customer touchpoints (Facebook & Instagram ad visuals)</li>\r\n                                        \r\n                                    </ul>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"200\" class=\"col-12 col-md-8\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                                <h4>We’d love to hear from you if you have:</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                            <ul>\r\n                                        <li>3+ years experience within the field of design</li>\r\n                                        <li>A strong portfolio showcasing work across a range of platforms: digital, print, paid, packaging and more</li>\r\n                                        <li>Expert knowledge of typography, grid systems, colour theory and composition. A background in motion graphics and illustration is a bonus</li>\r\n                                        <li>A passion for brand building and a strong understanding of how to maintain and evolve design systems</li>\r\n                                        <li>Advanced Creative Suite and Sketch knowledge. AfterEffects proficiency is a bonus</li>\r\n                                        <li>Previous experience at an agency or high end consumer brand preferred, but not required</li>\r\n                                        <li>Proven leadership and strong communication skills plus an ability to work cross functionally with ease</li>\r\n                                    </ul>\r\n                    