e the right fit for you to work with. Consultations generally take between 15-30 minutes and we do not charge for this service.</p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"200\" class=\"col-12 col-md-4\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                                <h4>DEPOSIT</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                           <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">We will collect a non-refundable, non-transferable deposit from you to reserve your tattoo appointment and drawing time. The deposit gets applied to the cost of the tattoo at the final sitting. The deposit will be forfeited if you decide not to get tattooed, do not show up for your appointment, have excessive last minute reschedules, or if you change your idea mid-process, requiring new artwork and additional drawing time. Should you need to reschedule, we ask 48 hours notice to keep your deposit and have it follow you to your new appointment time.</p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-delay=\"200\" class=\"col-12 col-md-4\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-element--round--box--border\">\r\n                                <h4>REFERENCE</h4>\r\n                            <div class=\"list-element\">\r\n                            <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For your consultation, please bring PRINT OUTS or email us any visual references or images you are attracted to that will help explain your vision for the piece you want to get. A little homework up front on your part really helps us draw the tattoo of your dreams!</p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n       